{"title":"使用Vue开发自己的背单词网站","uid":"87fc839f19a8a78008a9254dc83a200e","slug":"Vue-word","date":"2020-04-23T11:26:08.000Z","updated":"2020-05-09T01:58:59.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue-word.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200508140012.png","content":"<h2 id=\"开发的起因\"><a href=\"#开发的起因\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"开发的起因\"></a>开发的起因</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;大三上学期学习了前端和后端，感觉光是听听老师讲的，不能对开发项目有直观和更深入的了解，正好我也打算考研，背单词一直让我很头疼，就是没有动力，也没有好的方法，也尝试用过一些背单词的APP，比如百词斩，但是背完之后看图片还能选出来，脱离图片就想不起来，感觉就像是在背图片意思一样，用处不大就放弃了，后来买了iPad,用了欧路词典里的背单词功能，感觉比百词斩好很多，他是让你看单词，直接想意思，不会就自己点击不会，直到你看到单词就能想到意思为止。因此，根据欧路词典，大三上学期，我用SSM框架，以及LayUI开发了我的第一版PC端背单词网站。</p></blockquote>\n <span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;由于疫情，寒假在家待的时间太长，准备学点什么，之前就知道有Vue这么个前端框架，在深入的了解过后，才发现他是多么的方便，相比于JQuery，所以就学习了Vue，特别这个还是我们中国人开发的，更需要支持一波，关于Vue的作者尤雨溪，我在我的博客里也放过他的纪录片<br><a href=\"https://cjpnice.gitee.io/2020/04/07/Vue-Day6/\">Vue.js作者尤雨溪的纪录片</a>有兴趣的可以看看</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;所以，我又基于Vue以及MintUi和MUI二次开发的我的背单词网站，这次我将前后端分离，这也是目前的发展方向，后台我还是用的SSM框架，以后打算学习SpringBoot,将后台改为SpringBoot</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"体验网址（账号：cjpnice-密码：123456-也可以自己注册，但是没有数据，导入功能还没写）\"><a href=\"#体验网址（账号：cjpnice-密码：123456-也可以自己注册，但是没有数据，导入功能还没写）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"体验网址（账号：cjpnice,密码：123456,也可以自己注册，但是没有数据，导入功能还没写）\"></a>体验网址（账号：cjpnice,密码：123456,也可以自己注册，但是没有数据，导入功能还没写）</h2><p><a href=\"http://175.24.33.228:8080/\">word</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"暂时的效果\"><a href=\"#暂时的效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"暂时的效果\"></a>暂时的效果</h2><p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200430163154.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200430163215.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200430163340.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200424154252.jpg\"><br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200424154251.jpg\"><br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200424154250.jpg\"><br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200430163422.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"今后的计划\"><a href=\"#今后的计划\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"今后的计划\"></a>今后的计划</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"><