01:42:10.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:42:56.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vue-Vuex.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"Vuex的作用 VueX是适用于在Vue项目开发时使用的状态管理工具。试想一下，如果在一个项目开发中频繁的使用组件传参的方式来同步data中的值，一旦项目变得很庞大，管理和维护这些值将是相当棘手的工作。为此，Vue为这些被多个组件频繁使用的值提供了一个统一管理的工具——VueX。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":402,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":12,"path":"api/categories/Vue.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","count":13,"path":"api/tags/前端.json"},{"name":"Vue","slug":"Vue","count":12,"path":"api/tags/Vue.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"Java设计模式：代理模式","uid":"cac107c1646c31ee8c78ea59f7343e0a","slug":"Java-DesignPattern11","date":"2020-04-21T00:52:04.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:42:06.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java-DesignPattern11.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"text":"什么是代理模式 Proxy模式又叫做代理模式，是构造型的设计模式之一，它可以为其他对象提供一种代理（Proxy）以控制对这个对象的访问。 所谓代理，是指具有与代理元（被代理的对象）具有相同的接口的类，客户端必须通过代理与被代理的目标类交互，而代理一般在交互的过程中（交互前后），进...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.7k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":13,"path":"api/categories/Java.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"设计模式","slug":"设计模式","count":11,"path":"api/tags/设计模式.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}